24
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:07,000
Different perspectives on man and psychology.

25
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:09.720
- Then it becomes more and more practically directed.

26
00:02:09,720 --> 00:02:13,160
So we have to apply what we learned earlier in the program.

27
00:02:13,160 --> 00:02:19,600
